We need to windows machine.
Go to the BatchObfuscation file and create your .bat file
Open up a cmd
Go to the BatchObfuscation directory and write this
> obfuscator.cmd <your .bat file> 
HIT ENTER! 
As we can see the new .bat file name with "o"  for example: powershello.bat

If you want to see what happaned to the new file, you can change extension .bat to .txt an open it.
We can see Chinese Characters!

If you want to use Deobfuscation techniques
Use the same steps for Deobfuscating file.

